    <entry>
      <title>List集合根据某一个字段进行排序</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/09/List%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E6%AE%B5%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/09/List%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E6%AE%B5%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="List集合根据某一个字段进行排序"><a href="#List集合根据某一个字段进行排序" class="headerlink" title="List集合根据某一个字段进行排序"></a>List集合根据某一个字段进行排序</h2><h3 id="1、Collections-sort"><a href="#1、Collections-sort" class="headerlink" title="1、Collections.sort()"></a>1、Collections.sort()</h3><h4 id="升序："><a href="#升序：" class="headerlink" title="升序："></a>升序：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//升序排列</span></span><br><span class="line">Collections.sort(list, <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Comparator</span>&lt;Student&gt;() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">compare</span><span class="params">(Student s1, Student s2)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> s1.getAge().compareTo(s2.getAge());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="降序："><a href="#降序：" class="headerlink" title="降序："></a>降序：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//降序排列</span></span><br><span class="line">Collections.sort(list, <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Comparator</span>&lt;Student&gt;() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">compare</span><span class="params">(Student s1, Student s2)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> s2.getAge().compareTo(s1.getAge());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="多条件："><a href="#多条件：" class="headerlink" title="多条件："></a>多条件：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//多条件-先年龄升序、后分数升序</span></span><br><span class="line">Collections.sort(list, <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Comparator</span>&lt;Student&gt;() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">compare</span><span class="params">(Student s1, Student s2)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> s1.getAge().compareTo(s2.getAge());</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(i == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            i = s1.getScore().compareTo(s2.getScore());</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> i;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="日期："><a href="#日期：" class="headerlink" title="日期："></a>日期：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//日期集合List&lt;Date&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span></span><br><span class="line">Collections.sort(list, <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Comparator</span>&lt;Date&gt;() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">compare</span><span class="params">(Date s1, Date s2)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> s1.compareTo(s2);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-使用JDK8新特性-list-stream"><a href="#2-使用JDK8新特性-list-stream" class="headerlink" title="2.使用JDK8新特性 list.stream()"></a>2.使用<a href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=JDK8新特性&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020">JDK8新特性</a> list.stream()</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//升序排列</span></span><br><span class="line">list = list.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparing(Student::getAge)).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br><span class="line">list = list.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparingInt(Student::getAge)).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//使用lambda表达式</span></span><br><span class="line">list = list.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparing(e -&gt; e.getAge())).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//降序排列</span></span><br><span class="line">list = list.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparing(Student::getAge).reversed()).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//多条件-先年龄升序、后分数升序</span></span><br><span class="line">list = list.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparing(Student::getAge).thenComparing(Comparator.comparing(Student::getScore))).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-解决对字符串进行排序"><a href="#3-解决对字符串进行排序" class="headerlink" title="3.解决对字符串进行排序"></a>3.解决对字符串进行排序</h3><p>我的实体类中，需要排序的字段是用<a href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=String类&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020">String类</a>型就行存储的，但实际存储的都是数值</p><h4 id="原理："><a href="#原理：" class="headerlink" title="原理："></a>原理：</h4><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/671de69bccf0467e97127f6168c09af3.png" alt="img"></p><h4 id="原代码："><a href="#原代码：" class="headerlink" title="原代码："></a>原代码：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">List&lt;ShopActiveRule&gt; shopActiveRules = shopActiveRuleList.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparing(ShopActiveRule::getFavourableCondition).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="修改后："><a href="#修改后：" class="headerlink" title="修改后："></a>修改后：</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">List&lt;ShopActiveRule&gt; shopActiveRules = shopActiveRuleList.stream().sorted(Comparator.comparing(ShopActiveRule::getFavourableCondition, Comparator.comparingDouble(Double::parseDouble))).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
